==Printing Reports==
To prepare a report with details on drawing logs, you use the [HelpRoot_Construction\PJ_65_30_00|Drawing Log Details] ([~/?ScreenId=PJ653000|PJ653000]) report. On this report, you can view the details of all drawing logs or filter them by project, project manager, and discipline. You can also select the '''Current Only''' check box to display only up-to-date drawing logs.

