The next day Bill Owen went to a meeting with the customer to discuss a project. He took a taxi and paid $25 by the corporate card. ==Configuration Overview== For the purposes of this lesson, the ''Expense Management'' feature has been enabled on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\CS_10_00_00|Enable/Disable Features] ([~/?ScreenId=CS100000|CS100000]) form.{br}
