red on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PM_10_10_00|Projects Preferences] ([~/?ScreenId=PM101000|PM101000]). *'''Reject''': Changes the status of the cost projection from ''Pending Approval'' to ''Rejected''. *:This action is available if the ''Approval Workflow'' feature is enabled on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\CS_10_00_00|Enable/Disable Features] form and cost projection approval is configured on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PM_10_10_00|Projects Preferences]. *'''Release''': Releases the cost projection revision and updates the '''Projected Quantity to Complete''', '''Projected Quantity at Completion''', '''Projected Cost to Complete''', '''Projected Cost at Completion''' and '''Completed (%)''' values in the cost budget lines of a project. The cost projection revision is assigned the ''Released'' status.
