|AP303000]) form. *''Pending Email'': Emailing is required for this document, but it has not been performed yet. The subcontract should be emailed if the '''Send Orders by Email''' check box (on the '''Purchase Settings''' tab) is selected for the vendor on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\AP_30_30_00|Vendors] form. *''Closed'': All the ordered services have been received. *''Canceled'': The subcontract was canceled through the '''Cancel Subcontract''' action (on the '''Actions''' menu of the form toolbar). A subcontract with this status cannot be edited.
