etime'': The control is used to enter a date. *''Multi Select Combo'': The control is a list box with a check box against each attribute value so users can select multiple options. For this type, you can enter a list of possible values. *''Text'': The control is a text box in which the user can type text. For this type, you can specify an input validation option: an input mask or a regular expression.
