This report represents the printable version of American Institute of Architects (AIA) report prepared for the projects that have the '''Show Quantity in AIA Report''' check box cleared on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PM_30_10_00|Projects] ([~/?ScreenId=PM301000|PM301000]) form. The report includes AIA Document G702™–1992, Application and Certificate for Payment, and G703™–1992, Continuation Sheet forms. {br}

You generate this report for a particular pro forma invoice from the '''Invoices''' tab of the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PM_30_10_00|Projects] form, or the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PM_30_70_00|Pro Forma Invoices] ([~/?ScreenId=PM307000|PM307000]) form. Based on the value of the '''AIA Level''' box specified in the corresponding project on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\PM_30_10_00|Projects] ([~/?ScreenId=PM301000|PM301000]) form, the lines in the continuation sheet are grouped by project tasks (if ''Summary'' is selected in the '''AIA Level''' box), or shown as they are presented in the corresponding pro forma invoice (if ''Detail'' is selected).{br}

Depending on the date for which the AIA report is prepared, the report could include the retainage that has been fully or partially released in the middle of the project, or all released retainage at the end of the project.
