This report provides a sample release of partial lien rights when the current payment has been received and future payments are expected.[anchor|#_a67330aa-f48c-48e6-8450-7ecff7a5adea]{br}

See below for a description of each parameter on the '''Report Parameters''' tab of the report form. For more information about using other elements on the report form, see [HelpRoot_Interface\Report_Processing_Options|Reports].
==Report Parameters==
On the '''Report Parameters''' tab, use the following parameter to select the information to be displayed on the report:[anchor|#_3c87c6d9-6a9a-430c-8306-65cf2a23b30f]
*'''Lien Waiver''': The lien waiver for which you want to view the report. You can specify the lien waiver number or leave this box blank to view the report for multiple lien waivers.
